                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860111-31-off142 t17860111-31-crimeloc144"></join>, out of my pocket, I found the prisoner's hand in my pocket, and I run after him and caught him, and I saw him put the shirt in another man's hand.</p>

               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>

               <p>I was coming down Holborn-hill a gentleman took me, I had no shirt about me.</p>

